data.description: Charming 4-bed 2-bath home in Parkview Estates. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a formal living area, and formal dining room. The dining provides a pass through to kitchen, complete with a double oven, ideal for culinary enthusiasts. Adjacent to the kitchen is a cozy breakfast area, perfect for enjoying your morning coffee. The spacious living room features a brick gaslog fireplace. The primary bedroom, situated on the first floor, offers ultimate comfort with an en-suite bath and a generous walk-in closet. Upstairs, you'll find three additional bedrooms along a central hallway and a full bath. Nestled on a large corner lot, this property offers plenty of outdoor space for relaxation and recreation. A detached garage with a bonus storage room provides additional functionality and storage options. Sure to go fast! Schedule your showing today.
